id: pm-bhhe
title: "Expand aggregate group-by to support priority, status, assignee, tags"
description: "The aggregate command currently only supports group-by parent|type. Attempting --group-by priority returns error: 'Aggregate group fields must be one of parent|type'. For a universal PM tool, grouping by priority, status, assignee, sprint, release, and tags would be essential."
type: Feature
status: closed
priority: 2
tags[4]: agent-ux,aggregate,extensibility,pm-cli
