author: audit-agent
estimated_minutes: 120
acceptance_criteria: "Aggregate supports grouping by priority, status, assignee, tags at minimum"
parent: pm-5rjn
resolution: Aggregate command now accepts and executes extended group-by dimensions with deterministic grouped output.
expected_result: "pm aggregate supports parent,type,priority,status,assignee,tags,sprint,release group fields with tests/contracts/docs parity."
actual_result: "Runtime now accepts expanded group fields, completion/help/contracts text updated, and unit+integration+coverage verification passed."
